Transportation Button TODO Tips For Rishikesh\'s Trip Located in the Himalayan foothills, Rishikesh experiences a cool weather for most of the months. It acts as a great escape during the hotter months of March and April, and September to October. It is best avoided during the monsoon months of June to August due to heavy rainfall. So, the best time to plan an adventure trip to Rishikesh is from March to May and September to November. white water river rafting,, cliff jumping, waterfall trekking, and so on.
